{"tid":734010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"M記一有新人啲薯條就好鬼正","createTime":"2018-07-08T09:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T15:41:46.000Z","uid":186694,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"780225e5c5bf6acae29f71fc355ca01b1e3aecf7","tid":734010,"uid":186694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:21:06.000Z","msg":"(只限我屋企樓下個間)<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪啲老鬼做得耐唔怕畀人小<br />\n對待啲薯條好鬼hea<br />\n冇落鹽都算<br />\n啲薯條凍嘅<br />\n我入黎食M記係為咗薯條啊屌你個閪<br />\n<br />\n好撚在 一到有新人黎<br />\n個個都要揸正黎做<br />\n啲薯條變返熱辣辣<br />\n食完一定要lam手指嘅薯條<br />\n再用可樂杯洗手<br />\n<br />\n滿足"},{"pid":"9aeadd6026cca3cf0481a1a8e06abd1b3d9b1da7","tid":734010,"uid":146924,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:26:26.000Z","msg":"用可樂杯洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabdbc71718a53cf8967218265e399ce412e701b","tid":734010,"uid":132587,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"我之前是在麥當勞打工的，而我剷薯條的原則是：<br />\n<br />\n「幹你娘塞爆」<br />\n<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管甚麼公司虧損三小的，每次產的薯條就是一大包。小薯產成大薯，中薯產成巨薯。大薯買一送一，跟把整個薯條站的薯條全送給你沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月薯條虧損二十六箱，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"336e90f82d9df089acc4868563027b0fcda02234","tid":734010,"uid":124107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d7ea40560a3672e614b938e7a6d1c06baba78b8","tid":734010,"uid":128972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"老麥轉咗手之後 直程好似變咗第個國家嘅嘢咁難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fbc8bb3fec6cb5377c713bce39a5ff3c11effe","tid":734010,"uid":186694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aeadd6026cca3cf0481a1a8e06abd1b3d9b1da7","tid":734010,"uid":146924,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:26:26.000Z","msg":"用可樂杯洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite